What you need to know:  According to a letter from the Ministry of Education that was copied to all regional, county and sub county Education directors, the championship will start on June 30 at the grassroots and end on July 7 at the national levelKenya Secondary Schools Sports Association (KSSSA) National Secretary General David Ngugi confirmed that they had been asked to organise for the eventsAt the national level, the championship will be held at Kigari Teachers Training College (KTTC)